Summary:	VMMouse input driver for the Xorg X server.
Name:		xf86-input-vmmouse
Version:	13.0.0
Release:	1%{?dist}
License:	MIT
URL:		http://www.x.org/
Group:		Development/Libraries
Vendor:		VMware, Inc.
Distribution:	Photon
